description.en: Bitcoin Standard Hashrate Token (or BTCST token) aims to widen up the participation of Bitcoin mining to the open market. Each BTCST represents 0.1 TH/s of Bitcoin mining power and by staking it, holders of the token are entitled to receive daily distributions of Bitcoin mined.
